<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

   <%- include('.././layout/head') %>

<body>
    <h6>Hello, <br>Welcome ON Board!<br><a class="logout" href="/logout">LOGOUT</a></h6>
        <%- include('.././layout/header') %>
        <ul>
            <% textarr.forEach((text,uid)=>{ %>
               <li>
                  <p><%= text %></p>
                  <button class='dbtn' type='submit' id="add-<%= uid %>">Add</button>
               </li>
      
               <% }) %>     
           

           <form action='/dialogue-translate' method='GET'>
          
            <select name='dialoguelist' id='dialogue'>
               <% langs.forEach(lang=>{ %>
                  <option value="<%= lang[0] %>">
                     <%= lang[1] %>
                  </option>
      
                  <% }) %>     
            </select>  

           
   </li>
  

     
</ul>

<p class="dialoguebox" id='toogle'>
        Ahmad: Good morning, Xia.  How are you?
        Xia:  I am well, and you?
        Ahmad:  I'm great, thank you.  This is my friend Shalom.
        Xia:  Hey Shalom, it's a pleasure to meet you.
        Shalom:  Nice to meet you too, Xia!  
    </p>
    <p class="dialoguebox2" id='sports'>
            Andrew: Did you go to the football game on Saturday?
            Ryna: No, I had to work.
            Andrew: Aw, it was a really good game!
            Ryna:  Really, who won?
            Andrew:  The Huskies won. They beat the Cougars 47-16.
            </p>
    <p class="dialoguebox3" id='weather'>

            Deziree: This rain is awful, isn't it?
    Brian: The forecast said it would clear up after lunch.
    Deziree: I hope so, but at least it's warmer than where I'm from.
    Brian:  Really, where are you from?
    Deziree: I'm from Russia, it's freezing cold there!
        </p>

    <p class="dialoguebox4" id='food'>
            Server: Can I get you anything to drink?
            Customer: Yes, may I have a glass of water please?
            Server: Would you like to start with an appetizer?
            Customer: Yes, what do you recommend?
            Server:  The mozzarella sticks are very popular.
            Customer: Okay, I'll take some!
        </p>


